{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"So I work in marketing, which I love,"},{"time":3000,"text":"but my first passion was physics,"},{"time":6000,"text":"a passion brought to me by a wonderful school teacher,"},{"time":9000,"text":"when I had a little less gray hair."},{"time":12000,"text":"So he taught me"},{"time":14000,"text":"that physics is cool"},{"time":16000,"text":"because it teaches us so much about the world around us."},{"time":18000,"text":"And I'm going to spend the next few minutes trying to convince you"},{"time":21000,"text":"that physics can teach us something about marketing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24000,"text":"So quick show of hands --"},{"time":26000,"text":"who studied some marketing in university?"},{"time":28000,"text":"Who studied some physics in university?"},{"time":30000,"text":"Pretty good. And at school?"},{"time":32000,"text":"Okay, lots of you."},{"time":34000,"text":"So, hopefully this will bring back some happy,"},{"time":36000,"text":"or possibly some slightly disturbing memories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39000,"text":"So, physics and marketing."},{"time":43000,"text":"We'll start with something very simple -- Newton's Law:"},{"time":45000,"text":"\"The force equals mass times acceleration.\""},{"time":48000,"text":"This is something that perhaps Turkish Airlines"},{"time":50000,"text":"should have studied a bit more carefully"},{"time":53000,"text":"before they ran this campaign."},{"time":55000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":58000,"text":"But if we rearrange this formula quickly,"},{"time":61000,"text":"we can get to acceleration equals force over mass,"},{"time":64000,"text":"which means"},{"time":66000,"text":"that for a larger particle -- a larger mass --"},{"time":69000,"text":"it requires more force to change its direction."},{"time":73000,"text":"It's the same with brands:"},{"time":75000,"text":"the more massive a brand, the more baggage it has,"},{"time":78000,"text":"the more force is needed to change its positioning."},{"time":81000,"text":"And that's one of the reasons why"},{"time":83000,"text":"Arthur Andersen chose to launch Accenture"},{"time":86000,"text":"rather than try to persuade the world"},{"time":88000,"text":"that Andersen's could stand for something"},{"time":90000,"text":"other than accountancy."},{"time":92000,"text":"It explains why Hoover"},{"time":94000,"text":"found it very difficult to persuade the world"},{"time":96000,"text":"that it was more than vacuum cleaners,"},{"time":98000,"text":"and why companies like Unilever and P&amp;G"},{"time":101000,"text":"keep brands separate,"},{"time":103000,"text":"like Ariel and Pringles and Dove"},{"time":106000,"text":"rather than having one giant parent brand."},{"time":110000,"text":"So the physics is that the bigger the mass of an object"},{"time":113000,"text":"the more force is needed"},{"time":115000,"text":"to change its direction."},{"time":117000,"text":"The marketing is, the bigger a brand,"},{"time":119000,"text":"the more difficult it is to reposition it."},{"time":121000,"text":"So think about a portfolio of brands"},{"time":123000,"text":"or maybe new brands for new ventures."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"Now, who remembers Heisenberg's uncertainty principle?"},{"time":129000,"text":"Getting a little more technical now."},{"time":131000,"text":"So this says that"},{"time":133000,"text":"it's impossible, by definition,"},{"time":135000,"text":"to measure exactly the state -- i.e., the position --"},{"time":137000,"text":"and the momentum of a particle,"},{"time":139000,"text":"because the act of measuring it, by definition, changes it."},{"time":142000,"text":"So to explain that -- if you've got an elementary particle"},{"time":144000,"text":"and you shine a light on it,"},{"time":146000,"text":"then the photon of light has momentum,"},{"time":149000,"text":"which knocks the particle,"},{"time":152000,"text":"so you don't know where it was before you looked at it."},{"time":155000,"text":"By measuring it,"},{"time":157000,"text":"the act of measurement changes it."},{"time":159000,"text":"The act of observation changes it."},{"time":161000,"text":"It's the same in marketing."},{"time":163000,"text":"So with the act of observing consumers, changes their behavior."},{"time":166000,"text":"Think about the group of moms"},{"time":169000,"text":"who are talking about their wonderful children in a focus group,"},{"time":172000,"text":"and almost none of them buy lots of junk food."},{"time":175000,"text":"And yet, McDonald's sells hundreds of millions of burgers every year."},{"time":178000,"text":"Think about the people who are on accompanied shops in supermarkets,"},{"time":181000,"text":"who stuff their trolleys"},{"time":183000,"text":"full of fresh green vegetables and fruit,"},{"time":185000,"text":"but don't shop like that any other day."},{"time":188000,"text":"And if you think about the number of people"},{"time":190000,"text":"who claim in surveys"},{"time":192000,"text":"to regularly look for porn on the Web,"},{"time":194000,"text":"it's very few."},{"time":196000,"text":"Yet, at Google, we know it's the number-one searched for category."},{"time":200000,"text":"So luckily, the science --"},{"time":202000,"text":"no, sorry -- the marketing is getting easier."},{"time":205000,"text":"Luckily, with now better point-of-sale tracking,"},{"time":208000,"text":"more digital media consumption,"},{"time":210000,"text":"you can measure more what consumers actually do,"},{"time":213000,"text":"rather than what they say they do."},{"time":215000,"text":"So the physics is"},{"time":217000,"text":"you can never accurately and exactly"},{"time":219000,"text":"measure a particle,"},{"time":221000,"text":"because the observation changes it."},{"time":223000,"text":"The marketing is -- the message for marketing is --"},{"time":226000,"text":"that try to measure what consumers actually do,"},{"time":229000,"text":"rather than what they say they'll do"},{"time":231000,"text":"or anticipate they'll do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234000,"text":"So next, the scientific method --"},{"time":237000,"text":"an axiom of physics, of all science --"},{"time":239000,"text":"says you cannot prove a hypothesis through observation,"},{"time":241000,"text":"you can only disprove it."},{"time":243000,"text":"What this means is you can gather more and more data"},{"time":246000,"text":"around a hypothesis or a positioning,"},{"time":248000,"text":"and it will strengthen it, but it will not conclusively prove it."},{"time":251000,"text":"And only one contrary data point"},{"time":253000,"text":"can blow your theory out of the water."},{"time":256000,"text":"So if we take an example --"},{"time":258000,"text":"Ptolemy had dozens of data points to support his theory"},{"time":261000,"text":"that the planets would rotate around the Earth."},{"time":264000,"text":"It only took one robust observation from Copernicus"},{"time":267000,"text":"to blow that idea out of the water."},{"time":270000,"text":"And there are parallels for marketing --"},{"time":272000,"text":"you can invest for a long time in a brand,"},{"time":275000,"text":"but a single contrary observation of that positioning"},{"time":277000,"text":"will destroy consumers' belief."},{"time":280000,"text":"Take BP --"},{"time":282000,"text":"they spent millions of pounds over many years"},{"time":284000,"text":"building up its credentials as an environmentally friendly brand,"},{"time":287000,"text":"but then one little accident."},{"time":290000,"text":"Think about Toyota."},{"time":292000,"text":"It was, for a long time, revered"},{"time":294000,"text":"as the most reliable of cars,"},{"time":296000,"text":"and then they had the big recall incident."},{"time":299000,"text":"And Tiger Woods, for a long time,"},{"time":301000,"text":"the perfect brand ambassador."},{"time":303000,"text":"Well, you know the story."},{"time":305000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":311000,"text":"So the physics is"},{"time":313000,"text":"that you cannot prove a hypothesis,"},{"time":315000,"text":"but it's easy to disprove it --"},{"time":317000,"text":"any hypothesis is shaky."},{"time":319000,"text":"And the marketing is"},{"time":321000,"text":"that not matter how much you've invested in your brand,"},{"time":324000,"text":"one bad week can undermine decades of good work."},{"time":327000,"text":"So be really careful to try and avoid the screw-ups"},{"time":329000,"text":"that can undermine your brand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332000,"text":"And lastly, to the slightly obscure world of entropy --"},{"time":335000,"text":"the second law of thermodynamics."},{"time":337000,"text":"This says that entropy,"},{"time":339000,"text":"which is a measure of the disorder of a system,"},{"time":341000,"text":"will always increase."},{"time":343000,"text":"The same is true of marketing."},{"time":345000,"text":"If we go back 20 years,"},{"time":347000,"text":"the one message pretty much controlled by one marketing manager"},{"time":350000,"text":"could pretty much define a brand."},{"time":353000,"text":"But where we are today, things have changed."},{"time":356000,"text":"You can get a strong brand image"},{"time":358000,"text":"or a message"},{"time":360000,"text":"and put it out there like the Conservative Party did"},{"time":362000,"text":"earlier this year with their election poster."},{"time":365000,"text":"But then you lose control of it."},{"time":368000,"text":"With the kind of digital comment creation and distribution tools"},{"time":371000,"text":"that are available now to every consumer,"},{"time":374000,"text":"it's impossible to control where it goes."},{"time":377000,"text":"Your brand starts being dispersed,"},{"time":379000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":381000,"text":"it gets more chaotic."},{"time":383000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":385000,"text":"It's out of your control."},{"time":387000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":392000,"text":"I actually saw him speak -- he did a good job."},{"time":394000,"text":"But while this may be unsettling for marketers,"},{"time":396000,"text":"it's actually a good thing."},{"time":398000,"text":"This distribution of brand energy"},{"time":400000,"text":"gets your brand closer to the people,"},{"time":402000,"text":"more in with the people."},{"time":404000,"text":"It makes this distribution of energy a democratizing force,"},{"time":407000,"text":"which is ultimately good for your brand."},{"time":410000,"text":"So, the lesson from physics is"},{"time":412000,"text":"that entropy will always increase; it's a fundamental law."},{"time":415000,"text":"The message for marketing is that your brand is more dispersed."},{"time":418000,"text":"You can't fight it, so embrace it"},{"time":420000,"text":"and find a way to work with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":423000,"text":"So to close,"},{"time":425000,"text":"my teacher, Mr. Vutter, told me"},{"time":427000,"text":"that physics is cool,"},{"time":429000,"text":"and hopefully, I've convinced you"},{"time":431000,"text":"that physics can teach all of us, even in the world of marketing, something special."},{"time":434000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":436000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}